{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-2b30c3ab-2738-4766-ab6f-69783b7126f8-9\nfc_d0580f64-3038-96ba-ab5c-755cd52b4655_2","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"VOICEMAIL_|create_voicemail|voicemail","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求","caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-2b30c3ab-2738-4766-ab6f-69783b7126f8-9\nfc_d0580f64-3038-96ba-ab5c-755cd52b4655_2","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"VOICEMAIL_|create_voicemail|voicemail","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":30,"content":"- **`cardKind=voicemail` 永不进 `Board.pending`**；进信箱靠 attach/schedule 分流 + 物化（见 §8.4–§8.5）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"  | { kind: \"mailbox_open\"; agentId: string; voicemailId: string; cardId: string }","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"  // 信箱打开：听已物化留言；Resolver / beginCall 绑定该 voicemail 卡（entryMode=mailbox_open）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"**听留言路径（钉死）：** 用户/调试打开信箱条目 → `mailbox_open` → `beginCall`（`frozenCard` = 该 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡，`interactionMode=playback_only`）→ 播槽内 text/audioRef → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` 等）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 `exits`。**不推荐**壳自播完只打 flag、Host 另写无 Session 的 exits 捷径。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"3. `mailbox_open`：按信箱槽 `voicemailId` + `cardId` 绑定该 **`cardKind=voicemail`** Definition；**不**从 `Board.pending` 挑选；Session 强制 `playback_only` + `entryMode=mailbox_open`。播槽内已物化内容。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"   - **禁止**把 `cardKind=voicemail` 解析为待接通剧情卡（voicemail 永不在 pending）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":187,"content":"| `attach_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → Profile.Board 增加 pending；目标 voicemail → push VoicemailGenStack（**不写 Board**） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":189,"content":"| `schedule_call_card` | **分流**：目标非 voicemail → 写入 once intent，到点 `agent_outbound`；目标 voicemail → once intent，到点入栈/物化进信箱（**非**外呼） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":191,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | **废弃**：校验拒绝；运行时不执行新写。旧 stub 读路径可过渡，不得作为新写真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":206,"content":"### 8.4 attach / schedule 对 voicemail 的分流","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"| 非 `voicemail` | 写 `Board.pending` | `agent_outbound` 响铃语义（现状） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":213,"content":"| `voicemail` | push **VoicemailGenStack**；**禁止**写 Board | 入栈/物化进信箱；**禁止** `agent_outbound` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":217,"content":"- 把 voicemail Instance 写入 `callCards.board.byAgent.*.pending`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":227,"content":"1. 出栈；加载卡定义；确认 `cardKind=voicemail`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":230,"content":"4. 写 `Profile.telephony.voicemails[]`（text 与/或 audioRef）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":264,"content":"- 目标 **非** voicemail：越过后生成 `agent_outbound`（外呼响铃）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":265,"content":"- 目标 **是** voicemail：越过后入 GenStack / 物化进信箱（**不是**外呼）；见 §8.4。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":21,"content":"type CardKind = \"free\" | \"story\" | \"system\" | \"schedule\" | \"voicemail\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":50,"content":"| `voicemail` | **语音留言卡**：进信箱、听完走本卡 exits；**永不**进入 `Board.pending`；不可经普通 `user_dial` / `agent_outbound` 解析为待接通剧情卡 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":52,"content":"**`voicemail` 强制组合（校验 error，Studio 锁定 disable）：**","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"`context` 对 voicemail 仍是剧情/生成合同：物化端口消费 `speakableBrief` / `privateBrief` / `objective` 等；若 `assets.playbackClipId` 已有成品片，物化可跳过 LLM 直接引用。详见 [语音留言改造需求 §3](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":69,"content":"| `mailbox_open` | **信箱打开**：用户/调试从信箱条目进入听留言；**仅**与 `cardKind=voicemail` 配对 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"| `attach_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `activation?` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → Board.pending；voicemail → 进信箱生成栈） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":235,"content":"| `schedule_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `delay: { minMs, maxMs }` | 见下方 **挂卡分流表**（普通卡 → 延迟外呼；voicemail → 延迟进信箱） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":237,"content":"| ~~`create_voicemail`~~ | — | **已废弃**：校验 error / Schema 拒识；Studio 下拉删除。留言一律用 `cardKind=voicemail` + `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":254,"content":"| Effect | 目标为普通卡（非 voicemail） | 目标为 `cardKind=voicemail` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":261,"content":"未知 `effect` 名：校验失败，运行时拒绝执行。包内若仍出现 `create_voicemail`：校验 **error**，并指引改为 `attach_call_card` / `schedule_call_card` 指向 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":456,"content":"  | \"voicemail_listened\"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":28,"totalMatchedLines":28,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-2b30c3ab-2738-4766-ab6f-69783b7126f8-9\nfc_d0580f64-3038-96ba-ab5c-755cd52b4655_2","startedAtMs":"1784788157774","completedAtMs":"1784788157952"},"model_call_id":"b389604d-3268-439e-80