sContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":89,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-5eb31380-107f-4e72-b363-3f33d0cbb06e-10\\nfc_b7079a1e-7b95-927c-87da-ba6754448a80_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md\",\"offset\":200,\"limit\":80},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"  | { op: \\\"world_fact\\\"; factId: string; equals: boolean | string | number }\\n  | { op: \\\"variable\\\"; key: string; equals: boolean | string | number }\\n```\\n\\n编辑器用表单拼装条件，不手写代码。\\n\\n## 4. Effect Registry（v1 白名单）\\n\\n所有 effect 必须带稳定 `id`（包内唯一），供幂等 key 使用。\\n\\n```ts\\ninterface EffectBase {\\n  id: string\\n  effect: string\\n  /** 为 true 时该条失败则中止后续 effect（见 16） */\\n  critical?: boolean\\n}\\n```\\n\\n| effect | 参数要点 | 语义 |\\n|--------|----------|------|\\n| `attach_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `activation?` | 给角色挂 pending Instance（**引荐/带话用此 + 卡上下文**） |\\n| `unmount_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId?`（缺省卸该角色匹配卡） | 卸卡 |\\n| `schedule_call_card` | `agentId`, `cardId`, `delay: { minMs, maxMs  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":90,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-5eb31380-107f-4e72-b363-3f33d0cbb06e-11\\nfc_b7079a1e-7b95-927c-87da-ba6754448a80_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md\",\"offset\":140,\"limit\":100},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"| `story.effect.skipped` | 幂等跳过 |\\n| `story.effect.failed` | 执行失败 |\\n| `story.card.completed` | **effect plan 终态之后**（含 completed_with_errors / aborted） |\\n| `story.card.exited` | 可选摘要事件（exitId + plan.status） |\\n| `story.ended` | `end_story` |\\n\\n**禁止**把 `call.ended` 等同于 `story.card.completed`。\\n\\n事件只追加，不改写历史。Board 由 Executor 更新时**必须同时**写事件。\\n\\n动态出口见 [15](./15-动态出口与通话中工具事件.md)。\\n\\n## 8. EffectExecutor\\n\\n### 8.1 接口\\n\\n```ts\\ninterface EffectExecutor {\\n  execute(effect: Effect, ctx: ExecContext): Promise<EffectResult>\\n  executePlan?(effects: Effect[], ctx: ExecContext): Promise<EffectPlanResult>\\n}\\n\\ninterface EffectResult {\\n  ok: boolean\\n  skipped?: boolean\\n  error?: string\\n  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":107,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" deprecation of create_voicemail.\",\"session_id\":\"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784787316257}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-14\\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"语音留言|create_voicemail|mailbox_open|VoicemailMaterialize\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-14\\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_0\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-14\\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_0\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784787324479\"},\"model_call_id\":\"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-4-f8q0\",\"session_id\":\"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784787324407}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":163,"content":"[gbx] · 搜索 语音留言|create_voicemail|mailbox_open|Voic… in docs/AI和人类","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":166,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-14\\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"语音留言|create_voicemail|mailbox_open|VoicemailMaterialize\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/works