{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-93800fba-9deb-4af2-bb63-925e41035e97-22\nfc_e7f83b3b-75b0-9759-a22e-d761dae18b42_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","offset":45,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"|----|------|\n| `free` | 自由通话默认卡；每角色应有且仅有一份默认 FreeCallCard（可在角色库配置） |\n| `story` | 强约束剧情卡 |\n| `system` | 系统/媒介卡（过场播放、系统提示等） |\n| `schedule` | 调度卡；**磁盘落点按用途分两路**，见 §8.1（禁止混用） |\n| `voicemail` | **语音留言卡**：进信箱、听完走本卡 exits；**永不**进入 `Board.pending`；不可经普通 `user_dial` / `agent_outbound` 解析为待接通剧情卡 |\n\n**`voicemail` 强制组合（校验 error，Studio 锁定 disable）：**\n\n| 字段 | 必须 |\n|------|------|\n| `interactionMode` | **仅** `playback_only` |\n| `entryMode` | **仅** `mailbox_open`（界面文案「信箱打开」） |\n| `toolPolicy` | 必须等价 `deny_all`（与 `playback_only` 一致） |\n\n`context` 对 voicemail 仍是剧情/生成合同：物化端口消费 `speakableBrief` / `privateBrief` / `objective` 等；若 `assets.playbackClipId` 已有成品片，物化可跳过 LLM 直接引用。详见 [语音留言改造需求 §3](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)。\n\n### 2.2 entryMode\n\n| 值 | 含义 |\n|----|------|\n| `inbound_user_dial` | 用户主动拨该角色才激活 |\n| `outbound_auto` | 系统安排角色外呼用户时激活 |\n| `either` | 两者皆可 |\n| `mailbox_open` | **信箱打开**：用户/调试从信箱条目进入听留言；**仅**与 `cardKind=voicemail` 配对 |\n\n### 2.3 interactionMode\n\n| 值 | 含义 | 工具 | 用户语音 |\n|----|------|------|----------|","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":470,"fileSize":19662,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":45,"endLine":74},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-93800fba-9deb-4af2-bb63-925e41035e97-22\nfc_e7f83b3b-75b0-9759-a22e-d761dae18b42_1","startedAtMs":"1784788180013","completedAtMs":"1784788180195"},"model_call_id":"b389604d-3268-439e-80f5-928ecb5767ac-5-4f26","session_id":"3bb78126-6129-463f-92ce-cf543f7b8658","timestamp_ms":1784788180164}
