{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-28\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/validation/package/schedule.ts","limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n * 模块名称：validatePackage 调度 Effect 规则\n * 模块说明：从 validatePackage 拆出以降复杂度基线；读卡经 ContentPort。\n */\nimport { FREE_PACKAGE_ID, SCHEDULE_PACKAGE_ID } from \"../../constants.js\";\nimport type { ContentPort } from \"../../ports/contentPort.js\";\nimport type { CallCardDefinition } from \"../../schema/callCard.js\";\nimport type { ValidationIssue } from \"../types.js\";\n\nfunction push(list: ValidationIssue[], issue: ValidationIssue): void {\n\tlist.push(issue);\n}\n\n/** SCHEDULE_ONCE_CARD_REQUIRED：延迟外呼必须 agentId+packageId+cardId */\nexport function validateScheduleOnceEffect(\n\teffect: { id: string; effect: string; [key: string]: unknown },\n\tissuePath: string,\n\terrors: ValidationIssue[],\n): void {\n\tconst agentId = typeof effect.agentId === \"string\" ? effect.agentId : \"\";\n\tconst cardId = typeof effect.cardId === \"string\" ? effect.cardId : \"\";\n\tconst packageId =\n\t\ttypeof effect.packageId === \"string\" ? effect.packageId : \"\";\n\tif (!agentId || !cardId || !packageId) {\n\t\tpush(errors, {\n\t\t\truleId: \"SCHEDULE_ONCE_CARD_REQUIRED\",\n\t\t\tlevel: \"error\",\n\t\t\tpath: issuePath,\n\t\t\tmessage:\n\t\t\t\t\"schedule_call_card requires agentId + packageId + cardId（禁止仅 topicHint）\",\n\t\t});\n\t}\n}\n\n/**\n * SCHEDULE_RECURRING_*：裸 recurring / Story 上 recurring / 目标 kind。\n * 目标卡经 ContentPort.readCard（__schedule__ / __free__ / 故事包）。\n */\nexport async function validateScheduleRecurringEffect(\n\teffect: { id: string; effect: string; [key: string]: unknown },\n\tcard: CallCardDefinition,\n\tissuePath: string,\n\tcontent: ContentPort,\n\tworkspaceKey: string,\n\terrors: ValidationIssue[],\n): Promise<void> {\n\tif (card.cardKind === \"story\") {\n\t\tpush(errors, {\n\t\t\truleId: \"SCHEDULE_RECURRING_IN_STORY\",\n\t\t\tlevel: \"error\",","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":215,"fileSize":5532,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/validation/package/schedule.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-28\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_2","startedAtMs":"1784788200615","completedAtMs":"1784788200866"},"model_call_id":"b389604d-3268-439e-80f5-928ecb5767ac-6-12nf","session_id":"3bb78126-6129-463f-92ce-cf543f7b8658","timestamp_ms":1784788200875}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-29\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md","limit":90},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 08. 内容校验规则\n\n相关：[01](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [13](./13-工具与能力注册.md) · [14](./14-资源与媒体资产.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [03](./03-编辑器界面需求.md)\n\n`validatePackage(packageId)` / `validateWorkspace()` 产出 `ValidationReport`：`{ errors[], warnings[] }`，每项含 `ruleId`、路径、文案。\n\n**级别：** `error` 阻断导出与调试开跑（可配置）；`warning` 可导出，底栏提示。\n\n## 1. 包 / 磁盘\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `CONF_CARD_FILE_MISSING` | error | conf `cards[]` 有 cardId，无 `cards/<id>.s-card.json` |\n| `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` | warning | 磁盘有 `.s-card.json` 未登记进 conf |\n| `ENTRY_CARD_UNKNOWN` | error | `entryCardId` 不在索引内 |\n| `REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN` | error | 包内派生引用的 agentId（owner / effects / attach 等）不在角色库 |\n| `PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN` | warning | 遗留 `participants` 含不存在的 agentId（字段将忽略）；空数组或不写不报错 |\n| `FREE_PACKAGE_SENTINEL` | error | 试图把 `__free__` 当真实故事包目录创建或 load |\n| `SCHEMA_UNSUPPORTED` | error | schemaVersion 不兼容（见 [17](../技术设计文档/17-版本迁移与兼容策略.md)） |\n| `LAYOUT_IGNORED` | — | layout 旁车不参与运行校验（可存在） |\n\n**路径 B（角色全局化）：** `participants` 可选、非白名单。`validatePackage` 对 `collectReferencedAgentIds` 派生集合做角色库存在性与 free/social 校验；`ownerAgentId` 不在遗留 `participants` 但在角色库 → **不得** error。\n\n## 2. CallCard / 出口\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `PROMPT_SCENE_PATCH_HARD` | error | `promptScenes.patch` 含 objective/forbidden |\n| `EXIT_EMPTY_STORY` | warning | story 卡无 exits（创作建议至少成功+failure） |\n| `EXIT_NO_FAILURE` | warning | story 卡缺 failure 类出口 |\n| `EXIT_NO_RECOVERY` | warning | story 卡缺 recovery 建议出口 |\n| `EFFECT_UNKNOWN` | error | 未知 effect 名 |\n| `EFFECT_ID_DUP` | error | 包内 effect.id 重复 |\n| `PLAYBACK_NO_ASSET` | error | playback_only 无 playbackClipId |\n\n## 3. 工具\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `TOOL_UNKNOWN` | error | allowedToolIds 含未注册 id |\n| `TOOL_KIND_MISMATCH` | error | 工具不允许该 cardKind |\n| `TOOL_PLAYBACK` | error | playback_only 仍声明工具 |\n| `TOOL_DIRECT_EFFECT` | error | 试图标成通话中直接 effect |\n| `TOOL_INTRODUCE_GUARD` | warning | 引荐类工具目标无 `canIntroduce` |\n\n## 3.1 Schedule / 外呼意图\n\n落盘分工见 [01 §8.1](./01-CallCard数据模型.md)、[19 §3.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `SCHEDULE_ONCE_CARD_REQUIRED` | error | `schedule_call_card` 缺 `agentId`+`packageId`+`cardId` |\n| `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_CARD_REQUIRED` | error | `schedule_recurring_call` 缺 `scheduleCardId` 且缺 `cardId`+`packageId` |\n| `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_IN_STORY` | error | StoryCard 上挂 `schedule_recurring_call`（周期外呼归 ScheduleCard 宿主） |\n| `SCHEDULE_CARD_KIND` | error | recurring 目标不在 `characters/schedule-cards/`（或非法 `__free__` fallback）；**含**故事包内 `cardKind=schedule` 剧情节点冒充日常卡 |\n\n## 4. 资产 / 角色\n\n| ruleId | 级别 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `ASSET_UNKNOWN` | error | 引用不存在的 assetId |\n| `ASSET_URI_MISSING` | error | uri 指向缺失文件 |\n| `ASSET_KIND_MISMATCH` | warning | playback 引用了非音频类 |\n| `ASSET_PACKAGE_INLINE` | warning | 包内出现完整 assets[] 内联（应迁全局库） |\n| `SOCIAL_TARGET_UNKNOWN` | error | social.target 不在角色库 |\n| `NARRATIVE_DIALABLE` | error | `isNarrativeOnly` 但 `dialable: true` |\n| `NARRATIVE_NEEDS_NO_FREE` | warning | narrative-only 仍配置了 freeCardId |\n| `FREE_CARD_MISSING` | error | 非 narrative-only 可通话角色缺 freeCardId 或文件 |\n| `FREE_CARD_KIND` | error | free 卡 `cardKind !== \"free\"` |\n| `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE` | — | 运行时错误码，非包校验 |\n\n## 5. 验收\n\n- [x] error 阻断导出；点击问题可定位卡/文件（导出 API `hasBlockingErrors`；定位 UX 可增强）\n- [x] golden 包 validate 无 error\n- [x] `__free__` 哨兵不可当包路径通过校验\n- [x] `ASSET_URI_MISSING` 硬拦（meta 存在但 `uri` 文件缺失）；见 `VALIDATE_PACKAGE_ERROR_COVERAGE.covered`\n- [x] warning 主路径进 coverage：`CARD_FILE_ORPHAN`／`EXIT_*`／`TOOL_INTRODUCE_GUARD`／`ASSET_KIND_MISMATCH`／`NARRATIVE_NEEDS_NO_FREE`／`ASSET_PACKAGE_INLINE`\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":79,"fileSize":4695,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/08-内容校验规则.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":79},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-29\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_3","startedAtMs":"1784788200618","completedAtMs":"1784788200867"},"model_call_id":"b389604d-3268-439e-80f5-928ecb5767ac-6-12nf","session_id":"3bb78126-6129-463f-92ce-cf543f7b8658","timestamp_ms":1784788200876}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-26\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/tests/validation/wrong-number-act1.validate.test.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n * 模块名称：wrong_number_act1 validatePackage 回归（S8-3 · 路径 B 空 participants）\n */\nimport { cp, mkdtemp, rm } from \"node:fs/promises\";\nimport os from \"node:os\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport { fileURLToPath } from \"node:url\";\nimport { afterEach, describe, expect, it } from \"vitest\";\nimport { createEngineHost, hasBlockingErrors } from \"../../src/index.js\";\nimport { createFsContentPort } from \"../helpers/fsContentPort.js\";\n\nconst repoRoot = path.resolve(\n  path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)),\n  \"../../../..\",\n);\nconst dataSrc = path.join(repoRoot, \"data\");\n\ndescribe(\"validatePackage wrong_number_act1 (S8-3)\", () => {\n  let tmpRoot: string | undefined;\n\n  afterEach(async () => {\n    if (tmpRoot) {\n      await rm(tmpRoot, { recursive: true, force: true });\n      tmpRoot = undefined;\n    }\n  });\n\n  it(\"has no blocking errors with omitted participants\", async () => {\n    tmpRoot = await mkdtemp(path.join(os.tmpdir(), \"airpc-val-wna-\"));\n    const dataRoot = path.join(tmpRoot, \"data\");\n    await cp(dataSrc, dataRoot, { recursive: true });\n\n    const host = createEngineHost({ persist: false, content: createFsContentPort() });\n    await host.loadWorkspace(dataRoot);\n    const report = await host.validatePackage(\"wrong_number_act1\");\n    expect(hasBlockingErrors(report)).toBe(false);\n    expect(report.errors).toEqual([]);\n    expect(\n      report.warnings.some((e) => e.ruleId === \"PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN\"),\n    ).toBe(false);\n  });\n});\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":43,"fileSize":1485,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/tests/validation/wrong-number-act1.validate.test.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":43},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-ec436c81-6ad4-49b2-b7e0-7fed9e31e094-26\nfc_30ee0585-500d-9cbb-8753-ea1aaef9e754_0","startedAtMs":"1784788200608","completedAtMs":"1784788200868"},"model_call_id":"b389604d-3268-439e-80f5-928ecb5767ac-6-12nf","session_id":"3bb78126-6129-463f-92ce-cf543f7b8658","timestamp_ms":1784788200889}
